data.description: Charming 3 bedroom 2.5 bath 1.5 story home. A solid brick home with lots of updates and finished lower level, located on one of Brentwood's most sought-after streets, offering great curb appeal. Inside you'll find a large living room with a wood-burning fireplace, original cove moldings, and windows that flood this room with natural light, including the open staircase to the second floor.  Dining room opens to the Living room through an arched doorway. Storage is a breeze in the kitchen with double pantries, 42" oak cabinets, stainless appliances, and great view of backyard through the window over the kitchen sink.  Breakfast room space currently used as a sitting room.  Main level primary bedroom has two closets.  Full bath complete the main level.  Upstairs find two bedrooms, lots of closet space and an updated bathroom-shower is amazing.  Finished L/L w/family room, half bath and a small office space.   Large level backyard-plenty of space for a basketball court and/or parking.
